name: 2.7.0-b4

name: 2.7.0-b3
body: Use this with the new cool plugin InterSites to get reports of number of users across your websites! http://plugins.piwik.org/InterSites

See all list of changes: http://piwik.org/changelog/piwik-2-5-0/

See changes to the platform and APIs: https://github.com/piwik/piwik/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md

Enjoy the decentralised analytics platform with built-in privacy!
